releaseNotes:
Add MD5, SHA1 text to string,url to short extension method.

eg.
public class Tools
{
   // get MD5 string value (upper case)
   public static string GetSHA1(string text)

   // get MD5 string value for upper case
   public static string GetMD5(string text)
}

and also available for extension method.
eg..

// get MD5 string value (upper case)
public static string GetSHA1(this string text)

// get MD5 string value for upper case
public static string GetMD5(this string text)

// get short url array, key: for encryption
public static string[] ShortUrl(this string url,string key = "Noeek")

// get short url, key: for encryption
public static string GetShortUrl(this string url,string key = "Noeek")

